    <authors>Vincent Hoogendoorn [Macaw]</authors>
    <owners>Vincent Hoogendoorn [Macaw]</owners>
    <description>
      MvvmQuickCross is a cross-platform MVVM pattern to quickly build 
      native iOS, Android, Windows Phone and Windows Store Apps with 
      shared C# code and Xamarin.
      MvvmQuickCross is lightweight and easy to modify: it adds no binaries,
      just one Visual Studio C# code snippets file and a few C# source files.
    </description>
    <summary>
       Quickly build cross-platform apps in C# with the MVVM pattern and Xamarin.
    </summary>
